From e5d79f8e04c7ed40ddc0e2ed0a215bc5d9fa841e Mon Sep 17 00:00:00 2001
From: Stefan Reinauer <stefan.reinauer@coreboot.org>
Date: Wed, 27 May 2026 21:37:19 -0700
Subject: [PATCH 1/7] uae: add QEMU-UAE plugin core

Add the QEMU-UAE headers, PPC CPU shim, startup path, slirp stubs,
and internal helper declarations needed by the plugin tree.

Wire the UAE sources into the QEMU 11.0 PPC softmmu build and add
the QEMU-side hooks used by the host emulator to synchronize with
CPU execution and drive the exported main loop.
